metadata.name: Love #313
metadata.description:
We all experience love at different scales, ranging from scarcely perceived instances of kindness to unforgettable affections shown to us by family and friends, pets and partners. Each of these moments link us to the same boundless and enveloping interconnectedness that persists across space and time: the infinite source of our deepest aspirations.

Like the feeling of simple bliss, ‘Love’ portrays the visceral radiant light and warmth of our innermost joys. By taking a moment to open ourselves up, these swirling worlds of weightless and seemingly infinite brush strokes invite us to slow down and dwell in prismatic intuitive swells.

In doing so, we may find the immense and omnipresent love that needs only our awareness to be felt.

__________

Press 1-9 to load at different scales (1 = 2,000x2,000 (default), 9 = 10,000x10,000)
When zoomed in, once the output is fully loaded, you can click and drag to move around the canvas
Press 'S' to save the image at the current scale
Press 'B' to toggle the background texture on or off
Press 'A' to toggle the loading animation (recommended for very large scales)

Created with p5.js
For third party license information, please see bundle.js.LICENSE.txt
__________
TENDER x teaboswell
May 2022

metadata.name: 🔸WOMAN 🔹LIFE🔹 FREEDOM🔸 #1017
metadata.description:
📅 To be recorded in history as the first event-based stamp collection of generative art on the blockchain. 

🟩🟩🟩🟩🟩
⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️
🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥

🔆The people of my country – Iran - have been chanting three words for several days: 🔸Woman🔸🔹Life🔸🔸Freedom🔸.

🟢For over forty years, we have fought for these beautiful words. Today, our most basic human rights are being ignored in Iran, and we fight for them every day. In my land, women fight and die but do not accept humiliation. Women and men stand shoulder to shoulder and fight together.

🟢I published this collection of 1401 generative tokens to show my support for the people of Iran. 401 tokens are reserved for other known supporters of this cause, and 1000 tokens are free to mint.

🟢All my works about Iran's freedom are royalty-free and will always be. Due to fxhash's limitation on royalty selection, I have selected it all for the minter.

✅After completing the token animation, you can save the image in the following sizes and apply the following color filters: 

⌨️ SPACE key   ⏩ No Animation

metadata.name: 🟧🟦 QT 🟦🟧 #45
metadata.description:
🟧🟦 Qt is a unique interactive PFP.

🔶As you move the mouse, QT eyes monitor your movements and react accordingly. If you're lucky enough to have laser eyes, you have a QT protecting you. There are several gift hearts and diamonds around you that you can pick up(There is no doubt that you will use them somewhere.). Your QTs bring nouns and behavioral adjectives with them. In the gift that's going around the platform, you'll find it.

A total of thirty rare groups are considered for QTs, making them unique among PFPs and allowing you to have diverse and exclusive QTs.

🔷QT is not just an NFT. To make significant events more enjoyable, QT is with you. All you need to do is own QTs and follow them. You will be surprised by QTs. 1011 girls and 1011 boys will mint in the first series of QTs in 2022. At the opening of the 2022 World Cup, the first QT Boy pieces were minted.

🤝Saleh.C4d and  ArashMP collaborated on QT.

✅ you can save the image in the following sizes:

⌨️ Key number 1️⃣ 1080 pixels

⌨️ Key number 2️⃣ 216  pixels


📃 License: (CC BY-NC-ND 4.0)

🅿️5️⃣ Built with p5js

📅 November 2022

metadata.name: Shift #53
metadata.description:
A generative algorithm honing the power of vertical displacement.

How simple may a generative algorithm be while simultaneously staying diverse enough for each art piece to be truly unique? Shift is the result of an exploration into this space, basing its existence on two principles — dissection and vertical shifting. Each variable in this art engine has been meticulously weighted, giving rise to high diversity and the possibility of epic combinations. 

Shift is a series of 888 unique pieces.

############

Display resolution is 1000x1400. Press ’s’ (in live mode) to generate a 6000x8400 hi-res image. This may take a while to generate depending on your hardware.

Original artwork by perkwerk * made with p5.js * 2022

Wanderer is an algorithm which uses hexagonal Truchet tiles to produce meandering paths of color. Originally created back in February, I am releasing it as part of this week's #fxhashturnsone celebration.

100% of primary sales will go the the Processing foundation.

Thank you to fx(hash) and to the entire generative art community.

metadata.name: Influence no.4: Linear Composition #46
metadata.description:
This is the latest set of the "influence" series. "Linear composition" is an exploration of creating a highly detailed abstract artwork using a very large matrix of small circular shapes that are colored based on a division algorithm, each having a different shape. It is also inspired by old dot-matrix printers that create a pattern of dots when printing. To see the artwork in detail, open it in high quality and zoom in. Various densities and more than 12 color palettes have been used.

-----------

- Add &density=2 to 12 to the live view URL to render the image at higher resolution.

- Press ’s’ on the live mode to save the artwork.

  Made with p5js.
